chart_description: This chart tracks the rate of HTTP requests made to the Kubernetes API server by Kubeproxy rest client, broken down by HTTP method (GET, POST).

dimension_descriptions.GET: The rate at which HTTP GET requests are made to the Kubernetes API server by Kubeproxy rest client.
dimension_descriptions.POST: The rate at which HTTP POST requests are made to the Kubernetes API server by Kubeproxy rest client.
